<p>* If you missed a deadline call the <a href="x28630.xml">Online Support Center</a> for more information.</p>
<p>If you meet the basic eligibility requirements for a BYU-Idaho Online Degree program and wish to apply, complete the following steps:</p>
<ol>
<li>Download a <a href="Documents/Admin_Offices/Online Learning/Online Application Tutorial1.pdf">step by step tutorial</a> (requires <a href="http://get.adobe.com/reader/">Adobe Reader</a>)</li>
<li>Go to <a href="http://besmart.com/">Besmart.com</a></li>
<li>Click "Apply Online"</li>
<li>Create a Net-ID and password. (We encourage you to use the same user name and password for Besmart and BYU-Idaho to avoid confusion.)</li>
<li>After choosing BYU-Idaho as your school, select "Online."</li>
<li>Begin the application process by completing Steps 1-3.</li>
<li>Submit the application online.</li>
<li>Go back to the application to check your status for completeness.</li>
<li>Check your email for further updates.</li>
</ol><ol></ol><ol></ol>
